    "description": "<strong>Sigil of Chaos</strong> 是一款充满动作性的砍杀游戏，游戏中敌人众多，极具挑战性，每个敌人都需要你高超的游戏技巧。<br><br>您将发现自己身处英雄不再的阿德尼亚王国。踏上从酷刑地牢到王室宝座的漫长旅程，克服欺骗和背叛，揭开谜团，解除诅咒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/86ea6751d64e0c19cf3f83c997b38b14.poster.avif?t=1770195857\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/86ea6751d64e0c19cf3f83c997b38b14.webm?t=1770195857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/86ea6751d64e0c19cf3f83c997b38b14.mp4?t=1770195857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您可以单人游玩，也可以召唤朋友与您一起冒险。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/a93fbe2d8e788514ba7752df4e424bb1.webp?t=1770195857\" width=617 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/66732922e57ed87ae10f019d8110b511.poster.avif?t=1770195857\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/66732922e57ed87ae10f019d8110b511.webm?t=1770195857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/66732922e57ed87ae10f019d8110b511.mp4?t=1770195857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>通过手机、平板电脑或个人电脑尽情享受！</ul><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044240/extras/c5108365d7fab7c15f56da80374e6223.webp?t=1770195857\" width=617 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_i